Module kivakit.core
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.map

Class CountMap<T>

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.map.CountMap<T>
public class CountMap<T> extends Object
Keeps a count for each key. There is some effort to keep results thread-safe, but true accuracy is not guaranteed.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
